Trains (Usborne Discovery)
Usborne | 2002 | ISBN 0794501745 | English | 52 pages | PDF | 18 MB

This book takes you on a journey through the history of trains, from early giants of steam to the latest bullet-shaped speed machines. Explores various trains and their uses, from steam locomotives to magnetic levitation trains, and includes Internet sites to visit that enhance the learning process
